{"tid":526706,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[唔好跳車]JR信越線昨日因大雪，超過400名乘客被困半路超過14小時，今早仍未能解決","createTime":"2018-01-12T01:07:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T02:16:03.000Z","uid":51271,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"e1933a3271f167470dabdaf7f970138841ecfffc","tid":526706,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:07:29.000Z","msg":"日本信越地區最近降雪量係平年十倍，有一班列車於昨日黃昏信越線兩個車站中間被大雪所困，當時車上有600名乘客，即使花上大量人力除雪仍未能令列車再前行。<br />\n<br />\n列車上暖氣，廁所維持正常，JR東日本於昨晚為乘客提供食水及食物，有三名乘客感到不適，亦有部份乘客由親友接走(主要係今日有中央考試)，JR東日本今晨考慮用巴士接走乘客，但要先確保乘客安全。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dzd--9c8WN0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDzd--9c8WN0&d=%2F3u2QRHOOrReLkGe8io5faEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=3d689e54\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Dzd--9c8WN0</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20180112/k10011285911000.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnews%2Fhtml%2F20180112%2Fk10011285911000.html&d=%2F3u2QRHOOrReLkGe8io5faEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=2d78d820\" target=\"_blank\">https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20180112/k10011285911000.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.asahi.com/articles/ASL1C7DLTL1CUOHB018.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asahi.com%2Farticles%2FASL1C7DLTL1CUOHB018.html&d=%2F3u2QRHOOrReLkGe8io5faEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=4a15b8a2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.asahi.com/articles/ASL1C7DLTL1CUOHB018.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.asahicom.jp/articles/images/AS20180112000059_comm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asahicom.jp%2Farticles%2Fimages%2FAS20180112000059_comm.jpg&h=643983fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n１１日午後７時ごろ、ＪＲ信越線の普通列車（４両）が新潟県三条市内の東光寺―帯織駅間で積雪の影響で立ち往生し、約半日となった１２日午前７時現在、運転は再開していない。同日早朝には家族らが近くまで迎えに来た一部の乗客が列車を降り始めたが、大半の乗客は車内に残っている。ＪＲは当初、約６００人としていた乗客について、現場で確認したところ、約４３０人だったと発表した。<br />\n<br />\n　車内は暖房が機能しているものの、立ったまま待っている乗客もいた。１２日午前０時すぎには、体調不良を訴えた中年男性１人が駆けつけた救急隊に担架で運び出された。ＪＲは午前２時４０分ごろに乗客に水を配り、同５時ごろには食料も届けたという。<br />\n<br />\n　ＪＲ東日本新潟支社によると、列車は雪をかき分けて進んでいたが、前部に徐々に雪が積もって動けなくなったという。周辺の道路も積雪が増えており、二次被害を防ぐため、バスやタクシーでの代替輸送も見合わせているという。"},{"pid":"27eccb1d2c8e8aefa986346d51c499397052b1b2","tid":526706,"uid":19287,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:10:57.000Z","msg":"即係原本以為架車可以撞開d雪？"},{"pid":"9f7fcac94b40675d6dbb1a36886607d37aaabe5c","tid":526706,"uid":51271,"like":38,"dislike":1,"score":37,"quote":{"pid":"27eccb1d2c8e8aefa986346d51c499397052b1b2","tid":526706,"uid":19287,"like":16,"dislike":0,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:10:57.000Z","msg":"即係原本以為架車可以撞開d雪？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:16:39.000Z","msg":"係，但雪太多撞唔開，2來而家新車太輕，E129系每卡比舊115系輕左四噸，自重輕o左咁多未必夠力去推開d雪"},{"pid":"4314c4b75f6a28064abb3a9e5ff7a60f0a4a5bb1","tid":526706,"uid":38523,"like":71,"dislike":2,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:18:55.000Z","msg":"律政司司長鄭若驊聲稱2008年購買屯門海詩別墅獨立屋時，屋內已存在地庫等僭建物，但《蘋果》發現鄭當年購入該單位時，向渣打銀行簽訂的按揭文件及樓契，並無提及屋內有地庫，且簽字保證物業詳情屬真實完整。多名法律界人士質疑，鄭若驊或已觸犯《盜竊條例》中「以欺騙手段取得金錢利益」罪；工黨昨日報警，促請警方徹查事件"},{"pid":"12845952bcf3c60eb0e3f589330c10371e8ca6ac","tid":526706,"uid":51271,"like":6,"dislike":2,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"4314c4b75f6a28064abb3a9e5ff7a60f0a4a5bb1","tid":526706,"uid":38523,"like":71,"dislike":2,"score":69,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:18:55.000Z","msg":"律政司司長鄭若驊聲稱2008年購買屯門海詩別墅獨立屋時，屋內已存在地庫等僭建物，但《蘋果》發現鄭當年購入該單位時，向渣打銀行簽訂的按揭文件及樓契，並無提及屋內有地庫，且簽字保證物業詳情屬真實完整。多名法律界人士質疑，鄭若驊或已觸犯《盜竊條例》中「以欺騙手段取得金錢利益」罪；工黨昨日報警，促請警方徹查事件"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:19:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"affc1efe35b2779efeda5de0c16f183b2cbd8f9e","tid":526706,"uid":8048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T01:22:00.000Z","msg":"港鐵工會指乘客走落路軌是雪上加霜　令服務進一步延誤<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/526020/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/526020/page/1</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"a6e8a96b72d7076c5dc27e3f22933d15d9b153bd","tid":526706,"uid":51271,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T06:19:23.000Z","msg":"被困列車於今朝十點左右終於成功駛離現場，車上200多名乘客終於解困。<br />\n<br />\nJR東日本就事件致歉，表示當時大風雪下除雪工作困難，強行開行恐怕會發生出軌意外。而被問到為何於晚上沒有安排巴士或的士乎接載被困乘客，JR東日本表示列車內當時電力供應沒有問題，但當時天氣惡劣，周圍積雪厚達77cm，加上環境漆黑一片，將乘客轉移到巴士或的士恐怕會發生意外，相對下滯留列車內較為安全。<br />\n<br />\n日本國土省已要求JR東日本就事件檢討運行情報通報同應急措施。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20180112/k10011286221000.html?utm_int=detail_contents_news-related_001\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnews%2Fhtml%2F20180112%2Fk10011286221000.html%3Futm_int%3Ddetail_contents_news-related_001&d=%2F3u2QRHOOrReLkGe8io5faEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=5fbc7ffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20180112/k10011286221000.html?utm_int=detail_contents_news-related_001</a>"},{"pid":"d03ece99f59af97dd5a39d1023916cd769100c61","tid":526706,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T06:22:57.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gCCYJwvUjAE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DgCCYJwvUjAE&d=%2F3u2QRHOOrReLkGe8io5faEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=72cd7972\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=gCCYJwvUjAE</a>"},{"pid":"f6787f9d7167c3d1d4e9851e696d439b902de43a","tid":526706,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"識道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45013c8dc06a600813c81b35ac7b1242b92e8f39","tid":526706,"uid":376,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"quote":{"pid":"f6787f9d7167c3d1d4e9851e696d439b902de43a","tid":526706,"uid":41818,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:00:20.000Z","msg":"識道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:04:26.000Z","msg":"之前有間廠雪條加10円價<br />\n全公司人出黎道歉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afdd87634467491dc5e14be785c5f34dc9410f37","tid":526706,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:19:27.000Z","msg":"咁凍<br />\n跳車有危險<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c2c8e4067ad42d5d00428129f454f634c2410bc","tid":526706,"uid":693,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:26:18.000Z","msg":"咁多雪又咁凍好難走到"},{"pid":"6b99d99dd126ef70039a535809f867f5ac392021","tid":526706,"uid":90166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T07:29:30.000Z","msg":"竟然冇香港人"},{"pid":"e388b703ea2855f4d34bdec8a7036658a81c854c","tid":526706,"uid":51271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T13:47:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20180112/k10011287081000.html?utm_int=news_contents_news-main_005\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww3.nhk.or.jp%2Fnews%2Fhtml%2F20180112%2Fk10011287081000.html%3Futm_int%3Dnews_contents_news-main_005&d=%2F3u2QRHOOrReLkGe8io5faEKYqckrLkk14koP0tj2xA%3D&h=f3152584\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www3.nhk.or.jp/news/html/20180112/k10011287081000.html?utm_int=news_contents_news-main_005</a><br />\n<br />\nJR東日本新潟支社部長向乘客致歉(港鐵馬屎坑去左邊呢又?)，並且解釋除雪車於當晚11時56分已即時作準備，於凌晨一點出動前往現場，但途中需要更換零件引致延誤。<br />\n<br />\n除左呢班車外，仲有三列列車因大雪關係o係中途站未能前進，總共有另外400名乘客於車內過夜。<br />\n<br />\n學者指出鐵路公司沒有於漆黑大雪環境中疏散被困列車上乘客決定正確，但應加強降雪量預測及除雪反應訓練<br />\n<br />\n內閣官房長官指國土交通省已要求JR東日本就事件檢討乘客救助，運行情報通報等措施，並指出日本仍有機會受大風雪影響，交通機構應確保運行安全，減少對乘客不便。"},{"pid":"3869ca8b98f61e5c0fa24fd5692cac4d5a714fc9","tid":526706,"uid":38461,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:08:43.000Z","msg":"人地日本就企喺乘客角度諗<br />\n香港就屌鳩乘客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91a56bea36099f6a682bbab4b3af8d35e858e783","tid":526706,"uid":51271,"like":47,"dislike":3,"score":44,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:13:17.000Z","msg":"BTW, 各大中文媒體記者你好，我幫你譯日文都唔好抄到咁足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"86fb53927c6e59228fe0eee66782ab7b7de4ab1b","tid":526706,"uid":164602,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:19:00.000Z","msg":"仲話全球暖化係假<br />\n天氣愈來愈反常"},{"pid":"233c6625910488ede16ce41c347ef4a42e1cd262","tid":526706,"uid":35430,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:30:54.000Z","msg":"大和民族同大中華根本係兩個層次<br />\n大韓直情捉都廢鳩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230d6cf66d919f85e5fc7ee3e6189fac32b6db4a","tid":526706,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:32:30.000Z","msg":"跳車行雪地？"},{"pid":"2298aca83837618e435dd6eaf450e0d0e82023dc","tid":526706,"uid":1518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T15:37:36.000Z","msg":"車上原來有廁所？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f833adfc750084740101c2d9302403d58d7cf9b4","tid":526706,"uid":45082,"like":4,"dislike":7,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"3869ca8b98f61e5c0fa24fd5692cac4d5a714fc9","tid":526706,"uid":38461,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T14:08:43.000Z","msg":"人地日本就企喺乘客角度諗<br />\n香港就屌鳩乘客<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T16:24:49.000Z","msg":"最少人地JR嘅乘客無亂咁走落路軌<br />\n條光頭佬係屌人自己走落路軌"},{"pid":"321f73a87359a093b31e23db0848abad5f3426bc","tid":526706,"uid":33213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"230d6cf66d919f85e5fc7ee3e6189fac32b6db4a","tid":526706,"uid":134323,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-12T